Package de.rwth.i2.attestor.strategies Description

Collection of all available analysis tasks, i.e. full configurations of the state space generation algorithm. This package contains general classes that are widely applicable to create and customize an AnalysisTask. Specialized versions based on standard hyperedge replacement grammars and indexed hyperedge replacement grammars, respectively, are found in the subpackages de.rwth.i2.attestor.strategies.defaultGrammarStrategies and de.rwth.i2.attestor.strategies.indexedTask.
